            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:9f64c38c-e37b-4507-a63f-a3ee01047839</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/maintenance_and_reliability/~3/GN1eamhWwto/internet-of-things</link>
