            <category>Videos</category>
            <category>Media Entries</category>
            <title>3 Steps to Reliability Excellence</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	In this 4-minute, 49-second video, Randy Heisler of Life Cycle Engineering explains using an A3 problem-solving tool to achieve reliability excellence. Learn how a three-step process in conjunction with A3 thinking can help you create awareness, perform an assessment to determine the current state and take action to achieve best practices.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	     &lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/maintenance_and_reliability/~4/A-rlEBbh1p4" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2013-12-18T10:29:45-06:00</a10:updated>
