            <title>Predictive Service Named One of America's Fastest Growing Companies </title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Predictive Service was recently named one of the fastest growing companies in America by &lt;em&gt;Inc.&lt;/em&gt; magazine. This marks the sixth year in a row Predictive Service has appeared on the &lt;em&gt;Inc.&lt;/em&gt; 5,000 list, which is a compilation of the nation&amp;#39;s 5,000 fastest growing private companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Based in Cleveland, Ohio, Predictive Service provides reliability consulting, integrated predictive maintenance (PdM) and maintenance repair solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Of the 5,000 companies on this year&amp;#39;s &lt;em&gt;Inc.&lt;/em&gt; 5,000 list, Predictive Service is one of only 355 companies to have been included on the list the past six years in a row.&lt;/p&gt;
