	&amp;quot;We were very pleased to learn that our company has been named to the well-regarded &lt;em&gt;Inc.&lt;/em&gt; 5,000 list once again,&amp;quot; said Predictive Service president and chief executive officer Don Frankel. &amp;quot;For the past several years, we have been honored with a spot on this prestigious list because of our sustained growth, and this year has been no exception. The addition of the new business groups to our overall operations, Reliability Consulting and Maintenance Solutions, has been an important impetus for our continued growth this year.&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
