            <title>Sprayon Launches Real Men of Maintenance Contest</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Sprayon Products and Krylon Industrial recently announced a new contest designed to recognize industrial maintenance professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	The &amp;ldquo;Real Men of Maintenance&amp;rdquo; promotion will be accepting nominations from July 2 to Sept. 30 for the best maintenance professionals. The top three entries (based on the number of votes and the quality of the nomination story) will win a $2,500 Bass Pro Shops gift card and a year&amp;#39;s supply of Sprayon and Krylon Industrial maintenance products for their facility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Nominations are submitted online in the form of a written story about why the candidate deserves to win, including how he solved a specific problem that affected the facility/organization in a particularly inventive/creative manner, how he employs best practices on a daily basis or implemented continuous improvement processes within the facility/organization, or how he demonstrates a comprehensive skill level, persistent attention to safety, proven leadership qualities and a superior work ethic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	All nominations will be evaluated for compliance with the official rules. Approved entries will be posted online for public voting. Everyone who is nominated will receive a free T-shirt (while supplies last).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	To be eligible, individuals must be employed in a maintenance capacity for one of the following trades: manufacturing, repair, operations, industrial, construction, welding, food processing and/or electrical work. To enter or for official rules, visit &lt;a href="http://www.RealMenofMaintenance.com"&gt;RealMenofMaintenance.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/maintenance_and_reliability/~4/40M-7MTi6M8" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
